{
  "video_id": "aoGJP02CtPA",
  "title": "Sharmeen Obaid Chinoy: Inside a school for suicide bombers",
  "es": 0,
  "json": [
    {
      "index": 1,
      "start_time": 16260.000000000002,
      "end_time": 18260.0,
      "text": "Today, I want you to look at"
    },
    {
      "index": 2,
      "start_time": 18260.0,
      "end_time": 21260.0,
      "text": "children who become suicide bombers"
    },
    {
      "index": 3,
      "start_time": 21260.0,
      "end_time": 23260.0,
      "text": "through a completely different lens."
    },
    {
      "index": 4,
      "start_time": 23260.0,
      "end_time": 26260.0,
      "text": "In 2009, there were 500"
    },
    {
      "index": 5,
      "start_time": 26260.0,
      "end_time": 28260.0,
      "text": "bomb blasts across Pakistan."
    },
    {
      "index": 6,
      "start_time": 28260.0,
      "end_time": 30260.0,
      "text": "I spent the year working"
    },
    {
      "index": 7,
      "start_time": 30260.0,
      "end_time": 32260.0,
      "text": "with children"
    },
    {
      "index": 8,
      "start_time": 32259.0,
      "end_time": 34260.0,
      "text": "who were training to become suicide bombers"
    },
    {
      "index": 9,
      "start_time": 34260.0,
      "end_time": 36260.0,
      "text": "and with Taliban recruiters,"
    },
    {
      "index": 10,
      "start_time": 36260.0,
      "end_time": 38260.0,
      "text": "trying to understand how the Taliban"
    },
    {
      "index": 11,
      "start_time": 38260.0,
      "end_time": 40260.0,
      "text": "were converting these children"
    },
    {
      "index": 12,
      "start_time": 40260.0,
      "end_time": 42260.0,
      "text": "into live ammunition"
    },
    {
      "index": 13,
      "start_time": 42260.0,
      "end_time": 44260.0,
      "text": "and why these children were actively"
    },
    {
      "index": 14,
      "start_time": 44260.0,
      "end_time": 46260.0,
      "text": "signing up to their cause."
    },
    {
      "index": 15,
      "start_time": 46260.0,
      "end_time": 48260.0,
      "text": "I want you to watch a short video"
    },
    {
      "index": 16,
      "start_time": 48260.0,
      "end_time": 51260.0,
      "text": "from my latest documentary film, \"Children of the Taliban.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 17,
      "start_time": 54260.0,
      "end_time": 58260.0,
      "text": "(Singing)"
    },
    {
      "index": 18,
      "start_time": 58260.0,
      "end_time": 61260.0,
      "text": "The Taliban now run their own schools."
    },
    {
      "index": 19,
      "start_time": 63260.0,
      "end_time": 65259.0,
      "text": "They target poor families"
    },
    {
      "index": 20,
      "start_time": 65260.00000000001,
      "end_time": 68260.0,
      "text": "and convince the parents to send their children."
    },
    {
      "index": 21,
      "start_time": 68260.0,
      "end_time": 71260.0,
      "text": "In return, they provide free food and shelter"
    },
    {
      "index": 22,
      "start_time": 71260.0,
      "end_time": 74260.0,
      "text": "and sometimes pay the families a monthly stipend."
    },
    {
      "index": 23,
      "start_time": 76260.0,
      "end_time": 78260.0,
      "text": "We&#39;ve obtained a propaganda video"
    },
    {
      "index": 24,
      "start_time": 78260.0,
      "end_time": 81260.0,
      "text": "made by the Taliban."
    },
    {
      "index": 25,
      "start_time": 81260.0,
      "end_time": 84260.0,
      "text": "Young boys are taught justifications"
    },
    {
      "index": 26,
      "start_time": 84260.0,
      "end_time": 86260.0,
      "text": "for suicide attacks"
    },
    {
      "index": 27,
      "start_time": 86260.0,
      "end_time": 89260.0,
      "text": "and the execution of spies."
    },
    {
      "index": 28,
      "start_time": 90260.0,
      "end_time": 92260.0,
      "text": "I made contact with a child from Swat"
    },
    {
      "index": 29,
      "start_time": 92260.0,
      "end_time": 95260.0,
      "text": "who studied in a madrassa like this."
    },
    {
      "index": 30,
      "start_time": 96260.0,
      "end_time": 98260.0,
      "text": "Hazrat Ali is from a"
    },
    {
      "index": 31,
      "start_time": 98260.0,
      "end_time": 100260.0,
      "text": "poor farming family in Swat."
    },
    {
      "index": 32,
      "start_time": 100260.0,
      "end_time": 102260.0,
      "text": "He joined the Taliban a year ago"
    },
    {
      "index": 33,
      "start_time": 102260.0,
      "end_time": 104260.0,
      "text": "when he was 13."
    },
    {
      "index": 34,
      "start_time": 106260.0,
      "end_time": 109260.0,
      "text": "How do the Taliban in your area get people to join them?"
    },
    {
      "index": 35,
      "start_time": 111260.0,
      "end_time": 114260.0,
      "text": "Hazrat Ali: They first call us to the mosque and preach to us."
    },
    {
      "index": 36,
      "start_time": 115260.0,
      "end_time": 118260.0,
      "text": "Then they take us to a madrassa"
    },
    {
      "index": 37,
      "start_time": 118260.0,
      "end_time": 121260.0,
      "text": "and teach us things from the Koran."
    },
    {
      "index": 38,
      "start_time": 121260.0,
      "end_time": 123260.0,
      "text": "Sharmeen Obaid Chinoy: He tells me that children"
    },
    {
      "index": 39,
      "start_time": 123260.0,
      "end_time": 126260.0,
      "text": "are then given months of military training."
    },
    {
      "index": 40,
      "start_time": 126260.0,
      "end_time": 131260.0,
      "text": "HA: They teach us to use machine guns, Kalashnikov,"
    },
    {
      "index": 41,
      "start_time": 131260.0,
      "end_time": 134260.0,
      "text": "rocket launchers, grenades, bombs."
    },
    {
      "index": 42,
      "start_time": 134260.0,
      "end_time": 138260.0,
      "text": "They ask us to use them only against the infidels."
    },
    {
      "index": 43,
      "start_time": 140260.0,
      "end_time": 143260.0,
      "text": "Then they teach us to do a suicide attack."
    },
    {
      "index": 44,
      "start_time": 144260.0,
      "end_time": 146260.0,
      "text": "SOC: Would you like to carry out a suicide attack?"
    },
    {
      "index": 45,
      "start_time": 146260.0,
      "end_time": 148260.0,
      "text": "HA: If God gives me strength."
    },
    {
      "index": 46,
      "start_time": 152260.0,
      "end_time": 154260.0,
      "text": "SOC: I, in my research,"
    },
    {
      "index": 47,
      "start_time": 154260.0,
      "end_time": 156260.0,
      "text": "have seen that the Taliban have perfected"
    },
    {
      "index": 48,
      "start_time": 156260.0,
      "end_time": 158260.0,
      "text": "the way in which they recruit"
    },
    {
      "index": 49,
      "start_time": 158260.0,
      "end_time": 160260.0,
      "text": "and train children,"
    },
    {
      "index": 50,
      "start_time": 160260.0,
      "end_time": 163260.0,
      "text": "and I think it&#39;s a five-step process."
    },
    {
      "index": 51,
      "start_time": 163260.0,
      "end_time": 165260.0,
      "text": "Step one is that the Taliban prey"
    },
    {
      "index": 52,
      "start_time": 165260.0,
      "end_time": 168260.0,
      "text": "on families that are large, that are poor,"
    },
    {
      "index": 53,
      "start_time": 168260.0,
      "end_time": 170260.0,
      "text": "that live in rural areas."
    },
    {
      "index": 54,
      "start_time": 170260.0,
      "end_time": 172260.0,
      "text": "They separate the parents from the children"
    },
    {
      "index": 55,
      "start_time": 172260.0,
      "end_time": 174260.0,
      "text": "by promising to provide food, clothing,"
    },
    {
      "index": 56,
      "start_time": 174260.0,
      "end_time": 176260.0,
      "text": "shelter to these children."
    },
    {
      "index": 57,
      "start_time": 176260.0,
      "end_time": 179260.0,
      "text": "Then they ship them off, hundreds of miles away"
    },
    {
      "index": 58,
      "start_time": 179260.0,
      "end_time": 181260.0,
      "text": "to hard-line schools"
    },
    {
      "index": 59,
      "start_time": 181260.0,
      "end_time": 183260.0,
      "text": "that run along the Taliban agenda."
    },
    {
      "index": 60,
      "start_time": 183260.0,
      "end_time": 185260.0,
      "text": "Step two:"
    },
    {
      "index": 61,
      "start_time": 185260.0,
      "end_time": 188260.0,
      "text": "They teach the children the Koran, which is Islam&#39;s holiest book,"
    },
    {
      "index": 62,
      "start_time": 188260.0,
      "end_time": 191260.0,
      "text": "in Arabic, a language these children do not understand"
    },
    {
      "index": 63,
      "start_time": 191260.0,
      "end_time": 193260.0,
      "text": "and cannot speak."
    },
    {
      "index": 64,
      "start_time": 193260.0,
      "end_time": 196260.0,
      "text": "They rely very heavily on teachers,"
    },
    {
      "index": 65,
      "start_time": 196260.0,
      "end_time": 198260.0,
      "text": "who I have personally seen"
    },
    {
      "index": 66,
      "start_time": 198260.0,
      "end_time": 200260.0,
      "text": "distort the message to these children"
    },
    {
      "index": 67,
      "start_time": 200260.0,
      "end_time": 203260.0,
      "text": "as and when it suits their purpose to."
    },
    {
      "index": 68,
      "start_time": 203260.0,
      "end_time": 205260.0,
      "text": "These children are explicitly forbidden"
    },
    {
      "index": 69,
      "start_time": 205260.0,
      "end_time": 208260.0,
      "text": "from reading newspapers, listening to radio,"
    },
    {
      "index": 70,
      "start_time": 208260.0,
      "end_time": 210260.0,
      "text": "reading any books"
    },
    {
      "index": 71,
      "start_time": 210260.0,
      "end_time": 212260.0,
      "text": "that the teachers do not prescribe them."
    },
    {
      "index": 72,
      "start_time": 212260.0,
      "end_time": 215260.0,
      "text": "If any child is found violating these rules,"
    },
    {
      "index": 73,
      "start_time": 215260.0,
      "end_time": 218260.0,
      "text": "he is severely reprimanded."
    },
    {
      "index": 74,
      "start_time": 218260.0,
      "end_time": 220260.0,
      "text": "Effectively, the Taliban create"
    },
    {
      "index": 75,
      "start_time": 220260.0,
      "end_time": 222260.0,
      "text": "a complete blackout"
    },
    {
      "index": 76,
      "start_time": 222260.0,
      "end_time": 225260.0,
      "text": "of any other source of information for these children."
    },
    {
      "index": 77,
      "start_time": 225260.0,
      "end_time": 228260.0,
      "text": "Step three: The Taliban want these children"
    },
    {
      "index": 78,
      "start_time": 228260.0,
      "end_time": 231260.0,
      "text": "to hate the world that they currently live in."
    },
    {
      "index": 79,
      "start_time": 231260.0,
      "end_time": 233260.0,
      "text": "So they beat these children --"
    },
    {
      "index": 80,
      "start_time": 233260.0,
      "end_time": 235260.0,
      "text": "I have seen it;"
    },
    {
      "index": 81,
      "start_time": 235260.0,
      "end_time": 238260.0,
      "text": "they feed them twice a day dried bread and water;"
    },
    {
      "index": 82,
      "start_time": 238260.0,
      "end_time": 241260.0,
      "text": "they rarely allow them to play games;"
    },
    {
      "index": 83,
      "start_time": 241260.0,
      "end_time": 243260.0,
      "text": "they tell them that, for eight hours at a time,"
    },
    {
      "index": 84,
      "start_time": 243260.0,
      "end_time": 246260.0,
      "text": "all they have to do is read the Koran."
    },
    {
      "index": 85,
      "start_time": 246260.0,
      "end_time": 248260.0,
      "text": "The children are virtual prisoners;"
    },
    {
      "index": 86,
      "start_time": 248260.0,
      "end_time": 251260.0,
      "text": "they cannot leave, they cannot go home."
    },
    {
      "index": 87,
      "start_time": 251260.0,
      "end_time": 253260.0,
      "text": "Their parents are so poor,"
    },
    {
      "index": 88,
      "start_time": 253260.0,
      "end_time": 255260.0,
      "text": "they have no resources to get them back."
    },
    {
      "index": 89,
      "start_time": 255260.0,
      "end_time": 258260.0,
      "text": "Step four: The older members of the Taliban,"
    },
    {
      "index": 90,
      "start_time": 258260.0,
      "end_time": 260260.0,
      "text": "the fighters,"
    },
    {
      "index": 91,
      "start_time": 260260.0,
      "end_time": 262260.0,
      "text": "start talking to the younger boys"
    },
    {
      "index": 92,
      "start_time": 262260.0,
      "end_time": 264260.0,
      "text": "about the glories of martyrdom."
    },
    {
      "index": 93,
      "start_time": 264260.0,
      "end_time": 267260.0,
      "text": "They talk to them about how when they die,"
    },
    {
      "index": 94,
      "start_time": 267260.0,
      "end_time": 270260.0,
      "text": "they will be received up"
    },
    {
      "index": 95,
      "start_time": 270260.0,
      "end_time": 272260.0,
      "text": "with lakes of honey and milk,"
    },
    {
      "index": 96,
      "start_time": 272260.0,
      "end_time": 274260.0,
      "text": "how there will be 72 virgins"
    },
    {
      "index": 97,
      "start_time": 274260.0,
      "end_time": 276260.0,
      "text": "waiting for them in paradise,"
    },
    {
      "index": 98,
      "start_time": 276260.0,
      "end_time": 279260.0,
      "text": "how there will be unlimited food,"
    },
    {
      "index": 99,
      "start_time": 279260.0,
      "end_time": 281260.0,
      "text": "and how this glory"
    },
    {
      "index": 100,
      "start_time": 281260.0,
      "end_time": 283260.0,
      "text": "is going to propel them to become"
    },
    {
      "index": 101,
      "start_time": 283260.0,
      "end_time": 286260.0,
      "text": "heroes in their neighborhoods."
    },
    {
      "index": 102,
      "start_time": 286260.0,
      "end_time": 289260.0,
      "text": "Effectively, this is the brainwashing process"
    },
    {
      "index": 103,
      "start_time": 289260.0,
      "end_time": 291260.0,
      "text": "that has begun."
    },
    {
      "index": 104,
      "start_time": 291260.0,
      "end_time": 293260.0,
      "text": "Step five: I believe the Taliban have"
    },
    {
      "index": 105,
      "start_time": 293260.0,
      "end_time": 295260.0,
      "text": "one of the most effective"
    },
    {
      "index": 106,
      "start_time": 295260.0,
      "end_time": 298260.0,
      "text": "means of propaganda."
    },
    {
      "index": 107,
      "start_time": 298260.0,
      "end_time": 300260.0,
      "text": "Their videos that they use"
    },
    {
      "index": 108,
      "start_time": 300260.0,
      "end_time": 303260.0,
      "text": "are intercut with photographs"
    },
    {
      "index": 109,
      "start_time": 303260.0,
      "end_time": 305260.0,
      "text": "of men and women and children"
    },
    {
      "index": 110,
      "start_time": 305260.0,
      "end_time": 307260.0,
      "text": "dying in Iraq and Afghanistan"
    },
    {
      "index": 111,
      "start_time": 307260.0,
      "end_time": 309260.0,
      "text": "and in Pakistan."
    },
    {
      "index": 112,
      "start_time": 309260.0,
      "end_time": 311260.0,
      "text": "And the basic message is that the Western powers"
    },
    {
      "index": 113,
      "start_time": 311260.0,
      "end_time": 313260.0,
      "text": "do not care about civilian deaths,"
    },
    {
      "index": 114,
      "start_time": 313260.0,
      "end_time": 315260.0,
      "text": "so those people who live"
    },
    {
      "index": 115,
      "start_time": 315260.0,
      "end_time": 317260.0,
      "text": "in areas and support governments"
    },
    {
      "index": 116,
      "start_time": 317260.0,
      "end_time": 320260.0,
      "text": "that work with Western powers are fair game."
    },
    {
      "index": 117,
      "start_time": 320260.0,
      "end_time": 322260.0,
      "text": "That&#39;s why Pakistani civilians,"
    },
    {
      "index": 118,
      "start_time": 322260.0,
      "end_time": 325260.0,
      "text": "over 6,000 of whom have been killed in the last two years alone,"
    },
    {
      "index": 119,
      "start_time": 325260.0,
      "end_time": 327260.0,
      "text": "are fair game."
    },
    {
      "index": 120,
      "start_time": 327260.0,
      "end_time": 329260.0,
      "text": "Now these children are primed"
    },
    {
      "index": 121,
      "start_time": 329260.0,
      "end_time": 331260.0,
      "text": "to become suicide bombers."
    },
    {
      "index": 122,
      "start_time": 331260.0,
      "end_time": 333260.0,
      "text": "They&#39;re ready to go out and fight"
    },
    {
      "index": 123,
      "start_time": 333260.0,
      "end_time": 335260.0,
      "text": "because they&#39;ve been told that this is"
    },
    {
      "index": 124,
      "start_time": 335260.0,
      "end_time": 337260.0,
      "text": "effectively their only way"
    },
    {
      "index": 125,
      "start_time": 337260.0,
      "end_time": 339260.0,
      "text": "to glorify Islam."
    },
    {
      "index": 126,
      "start_time": 339260.0,
      "end_time": 341260.0,
      "text": "I want you to watch another excerpt from the film."
    },
    {
      "index": 127,
      "start_time": 345260.0,
      "end_time": 347260.0,
      "text": "This boy is called Zenola."
    },
    {
      "index": 128,
      "start_time": 347260.0,
      "end_time": 349260.0,
      "text": "He blew himself up, killing six."
    },
    {
      "index": 129,
      "start_time": 352260.0,
      "end_time": 354260.0,
      "text": "This boy is called Sadik."
    },
    {
      "index": 130,
      "start_time": 354260.0,
      "end_time": 356260.0,
      "text": "He killed 22."
    },
    {
      "index": 131,
      "start_time": 359260.0,
      "end_time": 362260.0,
      "text": "This boy is called Messoud."
    },
    {
      "index": 132,
      "start_time": 362260.0,
      "end_time": 364260.0,
      "text": "He killed 28."
    },
    {
      "index": 133,
      "start_time": 367260.0,
      "end_time": 370260.0,
      "text": "The Taliban are running suicide schools,"
    },
    {
      "index": 134,
      "start_time": 370260.0,
      "end_time": 372260.0,
      "text": "preparing a generation of boys"
    },
    {
      "index": 135,
      "start_time": 372260.0,
      "end_time": 375260.0,
      "text": "for atrocities against civilians."
    },
    {
      "index": 136,
      "start_time": 376260.0,
      "end_time": 379260.0,
      "text": "Do you want to carry out a suicide attack?"
    },
    {
      "index": 137,
      "start_time": 379260.0,
      "end_time": 382260.0,
      "text": "Boy: I would love to."
    },
    {
      "index": 138,
      "start_time": 382260.0,
      "end_time": 385260.0,
      "text": "But only if I get permission from my dad."
    },
    {
      "index": 139,
      "start_time": 387260.0,
      "end_time": 391260.0,
      "text": "When I look at suicide bombers younger than me, or my age,"
    },
    {
      "index": 140,
      "start_time": 394260.0,
      "end_time": 398260.0,
      "text": "I get so inspired by their terrific attacks."
    },
    {
      "index": 141,
      "start_time": 398260.0,
      "end_time": 400260.0,
      "text": "SOC: What blessing would you get"
    },
    {
      "index": 142,
      "start_time": 400260.0,
      "end_time": 402260.0,
      "text": "from carrying out a suicide attack?"
    },
    {
      "index": 143,
      "start_time": 403260.0,
      "end_time": 406260.0,
      "text": "Boy: On the day of judgment, God will ask me,"
    },
    {
      "index": 144,
      "start_time": 406260.0,
      "end_time": 408260.0,
      "text": "\"Why did you do that?\""
    },
    {
      "index": 145,
      "start_time": 411260.0,
      "end_time": 415260.0,
      "text": "I will answer, \"My Lord! Only to make you happy!"
    },
    {
      "index": 146,
      "start_time": 417260.0,
      "end_time": 421260.0,
      "text": "I have laid down my life fighting the infidels.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 147,
      "start_time": 424260.0,
      "end_time": 429260.0,
      "text": "Then God will look at my intention."
    },
    {
      "index": 148,
      "start_time": 431260.0,
      "end_time": 437260.0,
      "text": "If my intention was to eradicate evil for Islam,"
    },
    {
      "index": 149,
      "start_time": 439260.0,
      "end_time": 442260.0,
      "text": "then I will be rewarded with paradise."
    },
    {
      "index": 150,
      "start_time": 445260.0,
      "end_time": 448260.0,
      "text": "Singer: ♫ On the day of judgment ♫"
    },
    {
      "index": 151,
      "start_time": 449260.0,
      "end_time": 451260.0,
      "text": "♫ My God will call me ♫"
    },
    {
      "index": 152,
      "start_time": 451260.0,
      "end_time": 454260.0,
      "text": "♫ My body will be put back together ♫"
    },
    {
      "index": 153,
      "start_time": 455260.0,
      "end_time": 458260.0,
      "text": "♫ And God will ask me why I did this ♫"
    },
    {
      "index": 154,
      "start_time": 460260.0,
      "end_time": 463260.0,
      "text": "SOC: I leave you all with this thought:"
    },
    {
      "index": 155,
      "start_time": 463260.0,
      "end_time": 466260.0,
      "text": "If you grew up in these circumstances,"
    },
    {
      "index": 156,
      "start_time": 466260.0,
      "end_time": 468260.0,
      "text": "faced with these choices,"
    },
    {
      "index": 157,
      "start_time": 468260.0,
      "end_time": 471260.0,
      "text": "would you choose to live in this world"
    },
    {
      "index": 158,
      "start_time": 471260.0,
      "end_time": 473260.0,
      "text": "or in the glorious afterlife?"
    },
    {
      "index": 159,
      "start_time": 473260.0,
      "end_time": 476260.0,
      "text": "As one Taliban recruiter told me,"
    },
    {
      "index": 160,
      "start_time": 476260.0,
      "end_time": 479260.0,
      "text": "\"There will always be sacrificial lambs in this war.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 161,
      "start_time": 479260.0,
      "end_time": 481260.0,
      "text": "Thank you."
    },
    {
      "index": 162,
      "start_time": 481260.0,
      "end_time": 483260.0,
      "text": "(Applause)"
    }
  ]
}